Package de.cellular.lib.lightlib.ui.view.gallery

Interface Summary
LLGallery.OnItemClickListener Event when user clicks on the shown items.
LLGallery.OnItemScrolledListener Event when the view has stopped moving items.
LLGallery.OnItemScrollListener Event when items are moving.
LLSlideView.OnItemClickListener Event when user clicks on the shown items.
LLSlideView.OnItemScrolledListener Event when the view has stopped moving items.

Class Summary
LLAsyncGallery Decorator for LLGallery that user can pass an array of URLs and the Gallery shows all items asynchronized.
LLGallery A smooth gallery with an indicator, left-right button controlling, left-right arrow controlling, and comment text under or upon.
LLSlideView A sliding view draws bitmaps with finger or without finger under control of timer.
 

Enum Summary
